<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7235533-the-way-of-kings"><img alt="The Way of Kings (The Stormlight Archive, #1)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388184640l/7235533._SY75_.jpg" />
